OL,6,FA sex attack victim killed herself
OL,7,Fwhile on the phone to Royal Mail
OL,8,Fbosses who had done nothing about a
OL,9,Fpredatory postman who had targeted her
OL,10,Fand four other women.
OL,12,FThe postal service had received
OL,13,Fseveral complaints about "creepy"
OL,14,FMichael Stewart's behaviour but no
OL,15,Fproper steps were taken to stop him
OL,16,Fand he continued to work.
OL,18,FOne of his victims took her own life
OL,19,Fduring a telephone call to a Royal
OL,20,FMail manager and another victim has
OL,21,Falso since died.
