OL,3,CSex attack victim of postman killed
OL,4,Cherself while on phone to Royal Mail
OL,6,FStewart, 63, of Windsor Crescent,
OL,7,FAmble, Northumberland, was convicted
OL,8,Fof 12 offences of sexual assault,
OL,9,Fharassment and exposure, in relation
OL,10,Fto five victims, after a trial at
OL,11,FNewcastle Crown Court was jailed for
OL,12,Fsix-and-a-half years on Wednesday (19
OL,13,FFebruary).
OL,15,FThe court heard "family man" Stewart,
OL,16,Fwho worked at Royal Mail for more than
OL,17,F20 years, hid his sinister motives by
OL,18,Fhaving a "kind word and cheeky smile"
OL,19,Fwith people he encountered.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/15
