OL,4,Cherself while on phone to Royal Mail
OL,6,FJudge Robert Spragg told him: "I pay
OL,7,Ftribute to all the women who had have
OL,8,Fthe courage to bring this case against
OL,9,Fyou.
OL,11,F"You hid what you were doing in plain
OL,12,Fsight, behind the facade of
OL,13,Frespectability, to allow you to get
OL,14,Faway with it for some time.
OL,16,F"Tragically they were not listened to
OL,17,Fproperly when they did report you.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/15
