OL,3,CSex attack victim of postman killed
OL,4,Cherself while on phone to Royal Mail
OL,6,F"You just carried on even after you
OL,7,Fwere warned or they told you to stop.
OL,8,FProper steps to stop you in your
OL,9,Ftracks were not taken."
OL,11,FJudge Spragg added: "No sentence I
OL,12,Fpass can undo the harm that has been
OL,13,Fcaused."
OL,15,FThe court heard the victim who took
OL,16,Fher life had made a statement against
OL,17,FStewart in December 2021 and she died
OL,18,Fby suicide in March 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/15
