OL,4,Cherself while on phone to Royal Mail
OL,6,FShe said in her statement that Stewart
OL,7,Fhad grabbed her shirt and looked down
OL,8,Fat her breasts, kissed her and exposed
OL,9,Fhimself to her three times.
OL,11,FIn an impact statement in December
OL,12,F2021, she said Stewart's behaviour
OL,13,Ftowards her had affected her sleeping
OL,14,Fand eating and she was on medication
OL,15,Fto help her. She also said she was
OL,16,F"not a confident person" and was
OL,17,Fhaving thoughts of self harm and
OL,18,Fsuicide.
