OL,6,FA police officer who spoke to her in
OL,7,FNovember 2021 said she appeared "upset
OL,8,Fand badly affected" by her ordeal and
OL,9,Fhad given her advice on support
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FWhen the officer saw her again to take
OL,13,Fher statement on 10 December 2021, she
OL,14,Fsaid she felt suicidal because of the
OL,15,Ftrauma involving what Stewart had done
OL,16,Fand the Royal Mail response to it and
OL,17,Fshe was referred to mental health
OL,18,Fservices.
OL,20,FOn 19 January 2022 she told police she
OL,21,Fhad taken an overdose.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/15
