OL,6,FJudge Spragg said she took her life on
OL,7,F11 March 2022 at her home, addng: "She
OL,8,Fmade a telephone call to a Royal Mail
OL,9,Fmanager in a very distressed state and
OL,10,Fblamed her ill health on Michael
OL,11,FStewart's offending against her and
OL,12,Fhow this was dealt with by Royal Mail.
OL,14,F"She committed suicide during that
OL,15,Ftelephone call."
