OL,6,FJudge Spragg told Stewart: "Her own
OL,7,Fvictim personal statement referred to
OL,8,Fself harm and suicide and she was
OL,9,Factually on the phone to Royal Mail
OL,10,Fmanagement when she ended her life
OL,11,Fshowing a clear causal link.
OL,13,F"While this response was not
OL,14,Fpredictable, it was nonetheless as a
OL,15,Fresult of what you did.
