OL,6,F"It is impossible to know the full
OL,7,Freasons why someone chooses to take
OL,8,Ftheir own life but I repeat, had you
OL,9,Fnot behaved in this manner towards her
OL,10,Fit is clear she would not have
OL,11,Fsuffered the severe psychological harm
OL,12,Fshe did, leading to the loss of her
OL,13,Flife."
OL,15,FThe woman's family say their lives
OL,16,Fhave been "destroyed" by losing her.
