OL,6,FThe court heard one woman was sexually
OL,7,Fassaulted by Stewart, who she said was
OL,8,F"creepy". His attack on her was
OL,9,Freported and he was "suspended for a
OL,10,Ffew days" from his route.
OL,12,FThe court heard he showed the victim a
OL,13,Fpicture of his penis on his phone when
OL,14,Fhe returned to that round.
OL,16,FShe said in an impact statement she
OL,17,Fwas left "disgusted" and that Stewart
OL,18,Fturned from a "nice guy to someone she
OL,19,Fhad to hide from".
