OL,6,FA Royal Mail spokesperson said: "These
OL,7,Fcrimes were abhorrent and had
OL,8,Fsignificant, and in cases tragic,
OL,9,Fconsequences for the victims.
OL,11,F"Stewart abused his position of trust.
OL,12,FThis verdict reflects the seriousness
OL,13,Fof his offences. We would like to
OL,14,Fpublicly apologise to the victims,
OL,15,Ftheir families and to others who were
OL,16,Ftargeted.
OL,18,F"The protection of our colleagues and
OL,19,Fcustomers is our utmost priority.
OL,20,FFollowing this case, we commissioned
OL,21,Fan independent review.
